name: AeroLogic 777-FZN [D-AALH] Snowy Landing at Calgary Airport ᴴᴰ
description:
My first time seeing AeroLogic! And, to my knowledge, this is the first visit of an AeroLogic aircraft in Calgary. This bird was operating a special charter into YYC, carrying a load of Porsches, much like that Lufthansa MD-11F I caught back in December! Despite the fact that it was minus 25, I'm glad that I caught this beauty! ATC is included, enjoy this very white aircraft in a very white setting. 

Thanks for watching!
